These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
There are 5 different favourite colors: orange, blue, black, brown, yellow
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, aconite, amaryllis, azalea
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, blend, old-henry, oliveros
 1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 2. the oliveros-smoker is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 5. the person who growslily is the person who likes brown##1
 6. the person who likes blue is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the person who likes blue is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the person who growslily is the vegafina-smoker##1
12. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| Color   | blue  | orange | black | brown | yellow  |
| Flower           | bellflower     | azalea     | amaryllis  | lily   | aconite    |
| Cigar         | blend | old-henry    | havana | vegafina  | oliveros |

