.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, chinchilla, frog, goldfish
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, blue, aquamarine, pink, mauve
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, documentary, family, martial-arts
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, pall-mall, dunhill, bluemaster, bolivar
 1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 2. the dunhill-smoker is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the frog is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who likes blue##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Pet          | chinchilla        | goldfish | lizard     | frog      | mouse  |
| Color           | blue   | aquamarine | mauve    | pink | light-blue |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family     | martial-arts | adventure    | animation  |
| Cigar   | bluemaster     | pall-mall | siglo    | bolivar      | dunhill    |

