.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
5 different pets are kept: bird, fish, horse, lizard, snake
City: london, marseilles, rome, colone, boston
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, september, february, october, june
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person traveling to rome is the owner of the bird##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Pet         | fish | snake | lizard  | horse   | bird    |
| City   | marseilles        | boston | london | colone    | rome   |
| Birthday     | january   | february | june      | september | october |

