.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: spanish, chinese, mexican, pakistani, argentine
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, june, may, july, september
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, videographer, coach, mechanic, security-guard
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, taxi, van
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the dancer##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the mexican##1
 3. the videographer is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the dancer is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the mechanic##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the mechanic is on the left of the spanish##1
10. the argentine is the coach##1
11. the chinese is on the left of the argentine##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Nationality          | pakistani        | spanish       | mexican | chinese   | argentine  |
| Birthday   | september | may | june | november   | july |
| Job   | mechanic         | security-guard     | videographer | dancer | coach     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

