The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, firefighter, mechanic, photographer, security-guard
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, skydiving, puzzles, fishing, gardening
House: victorian, townhouse, wooden, palace, colonial
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the wooden house##1
 2. the wooden house is the mechanic##1
 3. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the colonial house is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the designer is the victorian house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the photographer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the palace house is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Movie-Genre          | drama    | superhero  | comedy | musical    | mystery      |
| Job           | security-guard | mechanic | designer  | photographer | firefighter |
| Hobby   | puzzles           | skydiving      | gardening      | fishing        | baking     |
| House         | townhouse         | wooden  | victorian   | palace       | colonial  |

