There are 5 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch, egyptian, french
5 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, bird, fish, rabbit
 1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 2. the owner of the bird is the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing bridge is the australian##1
 5. the french is on the far right##1
 6. the egyptian is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the dutch is in the middle##1
 8. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
10. the egyptian is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
11. the person playing bridge is the ritmeester-smoker##1
12. the owner of the fish is the british##1
13. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
| Cigar          | ritmeester     | havana  | alhambra | bolivar     | davidoff |
| Game           | bridge   | mah-jongg | billiard     | backgammon | domino |
