 4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the spanish##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the british is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 9. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the malaysian##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | drawing | singing | sudoku  | photography  |
| Nationality   | malaysian    | spanish    | british        | indian | egyptian     |
| City           | paris | berlin      | colone       | liverpool   | rome   |

