.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian, american, argentine, chinese
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, gospel, jazz
City: boston, berlin, new-york, liverpool, london
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, scooter, roller, bike, trike
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the chinese is on the left of the nigerian##1
 5. the person traveling to london is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the chinese##1
 7. the malaysian is the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the american is the fan of country##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to boston is the fan of jazz##1
11. the person driving the bike is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the chinese is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
13. the argentine is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
