.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, lemonade, milk, tea
House: craftsman, victorian, art-deco, ranch-style, tower
5 different games are played: bridge, snooker, poker, billiard, monopoly
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, vegafina, alhambra, blend, dunhill
 1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 3. the tower house is the chaman-smoker##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the victorian house##1
 8. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing poker##1
11. the craftsman house is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the art-deco house is the person drinking tea##1
13. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
