.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, cain, tiparillo, siglo, vegafina
The people have 5 different jobs:  engineer, pilot, analyst, designer, accountant
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, british, italian, polish, thai
5 different pets are kept: mouse, horse, rabbit, lizard, ferret
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the designer is the owner of the mouse##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the designer##1
 4. the engineer is the thai##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 7. the analyst is the british##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
10. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the engineer is on the far right##1
12. the accountant is in the middle##1
13. the argentine is the siglo-smoker##1
14. the polish is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Cigar      | cain | siglo   | tiparillo    | pall-mall       | vegafina |
| Job   | analyst           | pilot   | accountant   | designer       | engineer  |
| Nationality   | british       | argentine | italian | polish     | thai   |
| Pet     | rabbit    | horse   | lizard   | mouse | ferret   |

 